{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_skgoat_set_1", "eventName": "額外的工作", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "額外的工作", "storyInfo": "作為羅德島極少數的地質學專家，地靈獨自承擔起了相當一部分的工作。當她休息的時候，還是儘量不要“親自”去打擾她為妙。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_room_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這個地方節奏有點亂了。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  琴鍵很重，後面速度一快是不是就有點跟不上？", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  有一點，不過我能克服的。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  多練習就好。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  今天練得夠多了，你的姿勢已經開始變形。以這種變形的姿勢繼續練習下去，反而會起到不好的效果。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  歇一歇吧， 你的進步已經很大了。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但下一課又不知道得什麼時候。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  如果我有一天也能像地靈前輩一樣會彈琴就好了！", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你很有天賦，一定會有那天的。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗨！地靈！", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  博士讓我來找......", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.4}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯？怎麼艾雅法拉也在這！", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我在教阿黛爾彈琴。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我以為這算是你的保留技能。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒必要保留。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  為什麼？", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  就算是那個音樂院校雲集的萊塔尼亞，也不會強迫每個人都學音樂吧。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  再說，我們是在羅德島上呀，不會樂器也沒什麼關係吧。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  羅德島其實也沒什麼適合萊塔尼亞人的娛樂設施。業餘時間學點樂器既是休閒，又能讓人在這樣的日子裡感受到片刻的安寧。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  而且在萊塔尼亞，一個擁有較高音樂素養的人，會被認為擁有更高水準的教育。這是在聚集區內的感染者難以擁有的。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 20.0, "ypos": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.1}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  （學會音樂這一技之長，日後去萊塔尼亞，隱瞞感染者身份也比較方便。）", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 30.0, "ypos": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.1}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  （地靈前輩在說什麼我已經完全聽不清楚啦！）", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 60.0, "ypos": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  好癢！知道了！知道了！", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  教阿黛爾也是為了提前做個試驗，方便以後教其他人的時候安排課程時間。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不過艾雅法拉學得還挺快。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我上次回來大概是多久前？也沒多久吧。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  現在就已經能彈得像模像樣了。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  現在才是第三次課，已經能斷斷續續彈這首高盧語命名的《月光曲》了。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我也沒想到，阿黛爾在音樂方面也那麼有天賦，真讓人羡慕。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  美妙的音樂，能讓我們在如今的歲月裡，在殘餘的生命中，多少也感知到一點點美好。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我覺得音樂很有趣，以前我爸爸媽媽也會教我，但是是和這個不一樣的萊塔尼亞樂器。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  可是這個琴鍵真的好沉重，速度一快就跟不上了！", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  真好聽啊。這個樂器與傳統琴的音色差別真大。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  每次聽都讓我感覺很震撼。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  普羅旺斯姐姐！聽我說，這個樂器原本可大了。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我以前沒彈過，但我在我媽媽教書的學校裡見過。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  大概有大禮堂的一整面牆那麼大！", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  現在的這個是用傳統的琴改造而來的。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  要盡可能地還原音色，還要縮小尺寸，其實做出了很多妥協。琴鍵如此沉重，就是妥協的結果。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  如果你能聽到真傢伙的聲音，那肯定還要震撼。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這麼說你是要帶我去你老家旅遊？", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  好期待！", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我老家不過是萊塔尼亞某個窮鄉僻壤裡的村子而已，可沒這個。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  對了！差點把正事給忘了。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  博士拜託我找你來著，要我把這份東西給你。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哦？麻煩的事情又要來了。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你手裡的是......又是要填的地質分析報告？", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$g_card_10cardsrelease", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  讓我看看。嗯......需要羅德島前方航線的可通過性地質報告......還需要近期附近天災發生可能性報告......", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$g_card_10cardsrelease", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  以及五份地質樣本的分析，需要對其所屬年代以及礦物質構成進行鑑別......", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  博士有說這些大概是什麼時候要嗎？", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  後天。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  後天就要？", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這些工作即使讓一個三人的專業小組來處理都需要至少兩天。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  羅德島並沒有這麼多的地質學專業人員。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  而且，作為醫療企業，羅德島現在沒有，今後也沒有成立地質實驗室的計畫。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  總結，我們缺少人力且缺少設備，且將會長期處於這種狀態。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  地靈前輩！要不要我也來幫忙！", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  也不用那麼擔心。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  有我在，沒問題的。阿黛爾，你還是多放鬆放鬆，休息休息，交給我吧。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  地靈前輩，今天我已經休、休息了很久了！", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  後天你還要和巴蒂一起外出工作不是嗎？好好休息，我的工作我也能處理好的。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不過這次我沒法陪你一起去了，你的助聽器工作狀態如何？", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  在羅德島的室內環境下暫時沒什麼問題。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  室外的話，希望也不會有什麼問題。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那就好，如果外出需要一些設備支援，你可以去找你的另一個前輩說說。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那傢伙雖然是個工作狂，但也一直很關心你的。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯......但{@nickname}前輩一直很忙。我、我怕打擾到前輩。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒關係，我會在出發前把要準備的都準備妥當的。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯。我今天也打算先舒舒服服睡一覺，準備好充足的精神，明天起來再開工。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不是人手不夠嗎，這樣也來得及？", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  充足的休息，以及適當的娛樂，才能保障在上班的時候能夠百分之百投入注意力。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  尤其這類研究的工作，原本專注半小時能解決的問題，在身心俱疲的情況下可能通宵好幾天都毫無進展。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  當然這份工作還是得加班一下，至於加班費......", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  博士剛才拍著胸脯說加班費會按標準給的。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那最好。反正只要沒有額外的工作，我就來得及。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那正好，我這裡也需要一份報告！", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你......", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嘿嘿，麻煩你啦！反正都已經要加班了！", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這次又是什麼？", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  老樣子啦，老樣子。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  還是天災信使工作參考用的地質分析報告。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  樣本呢？", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  已經放在你的樣本儲存盒裡了。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那麼你又是什麼時候要？", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  越快越好！", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  說得挺輕巧。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你作為一個天災信使，鮮有在羅德島本艦待著的時候。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  每次回來，就塞給我一堆工作。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你是不是忘了除同事的關係外，我們也是朋友？", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒辦法，天災信使的工作就是這樣嘛。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我現在也只是回來一趟。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  很快要走嗎？", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是啊，工作還沒結束。我就回來要份報告，要到就得走了。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  需求。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  儘量讓看這份報告的傢伙一頭霧水，以至於放棄理解。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  專業點是吧，沒問題。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  什麼是一頭霧水的報告啊？", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這是一種天災信使專用的報告啦，不過大多數時間並不是給我們這些天災信使看的。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  大多數時間，是給雇主或是當地管事的人看的。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  由天災信使邀請學者提供各類資料分析，讓對方根據資料自行判斷是否需要遷移躲避天災，也是一種工作方式。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這樣，誤報的風險就轉移到了做判斷的對方身上。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  在這種情況下，如果天災沒有發生，因為城鎮遷移而造成的經濟損失，就無法怪罪到天災信使頭上來。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  畢竟天災信使也只是普通人，有正常人該有的所有心情，也會犯錯。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  有的天災信使因為一次誤報進而失去信心，自我懷疑，最後不再從事這份工作。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  出錯是很正常的。可是天災信使這份工作，犯一次錯要承擔的後果太嚴重了......", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這種轉移風險的模式，也是為了保護天災信使而誕生的。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不過，這樣就增加了資料分析方面的工作量。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  而且來來回回跑也需要時間，我只能幫到離羅德島較近的天災信使。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這樣也挺好，你就能有更多時間留在羅德島上。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  如果你還像從前一樣作為天災信使與地質學專家到處亂跑，我們可能一年都見不到幾次面。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這就是你揮霍見面機會的理由嗎？", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哎呀！", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  別嬉皮笑臉的！", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  當初建議我這樣做的，可是你啊！", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒錯，我不希望任何人重蹈巴赫曼老師的悲劇。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊！是那位古爾克私立學院的巴赫曼教授嗎？那可是萊塔尼亞有名的地質學家與音樂家，原來她是地靈前輩的老師啊！", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我的媽媽認識她。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  小時候，我過生日時她還正好來過我家。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  當然，她並不知道那天是我的生日，只是因為工作上的事情來找我的媽媽。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  知道是我生日後，就為我演奏了一曲作為禮物。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我記得她也能彈出非常美妙的音樂。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那也是我最崇拜的人。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  巴赫曼教授發生什麼事了嗎？", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  一個地方貴族指名雇傭她作為天災信使，她也給出了專業的分析。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  巴赫曼教授居然也是天災信使？！", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  雖然不像她的地質學家與音樂家身份那麼有名，但她確實是一位天災信使。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  貴族要求巴赫曼老師給出一個最終的，明確的答案——天災究竟會不會發生......", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......居民究竟要不要轉移。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  巴赫曼老師其實是位很純粹的萊塔尼亞學者，雖然很年長，卻沒有什麼城府。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  她所考慮的，都是最保守的方式。因此，對當地地質環境進行分析後，她建議居民還是立刻轉移為好。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  結果，天災並沒有發生。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  當地居民回到原來的地方，他們的作物爛在了地裡。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  僅剩的那些糧食，必須上交給貴族。於是，他們難免要忍饑挨餓。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  在收繳糧食時，面對蜷縮著的哭乞的居民們，貴族的喉舌們如是說......", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  “都是那個巴赫曼的錯，如果她沒有誤報，我們就不需要轉移避險。”", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  “都是因為她，才害你們這樣。”", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  “都是她的錯。”", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  民眾的怒火被點燃了。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  他們趁夜襲擊了巴赫曼老師，拿石頭把她砸暈，綁起來，要把她燒死。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ——！", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  連那位巴赫曼教授都......", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  所以你不希望任何人再遇到這樣的事情。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你想透過學識，而非武力，來保護他人。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  前輩喜歡地質學是因為這個原因，用學識來保護人？", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不，不是。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我起初學地質學的目的很簡單。和你不同，我並沒有足夠的法術天賦。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  感染礦石病後我現有的源石技藝變強了，但這不代表我的天賦也變強了。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  在源石技藝方面，我太笨拙了。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你可真是太謙虛了，這都算笨拙的話我一定傻到離譜。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  後半句倒不假。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  以我的天賦，固執地學習源石技藝是沒有用的。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  小時候我很聰明，父母給了我很大期望。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我從小讀很多書，超前地掌握了各種基礎源石技藝及其理論技巧。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  周圍的人都認為我以後必將有所出息。我的父母期望我能改變我們家族的地位，讓我們能搬進城裡。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但隨著我慢慢長大，要學的東西越來越複雜，我發現光“聰明”是沒有用的。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  就算理論了然於胸，沒有天賦就是沒有天賦，做不到就是做不到。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  地質學不一樣。對我而言，只要努力學習，我能在這裡找到自己......", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  找到父母原本期望的那個我。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  所以其實一開始你是不得不學習地質學？", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不是“不得不”，而是巴赫曼老師的地質學課程，在我最失落絕望的時刻拯救了我，接納了我。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  從那時起，我才開始學習地質學，通過一個個小小的成就，逐漸愛上它。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這是一個有我容身之處的地方，一個家。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  可是地質學聽起來還是挺枯燥的。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  正相反，就算這片大地上的所有書疊起來，都是有窮盡的。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  地質學，是一個無窮無盡的書架。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  每一次實地考察，都能從勘探中找到不同的故事，瞭解每個地方的歷史演變。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  就好像它們在對我低語......", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  地質學就是一座無窮盡的自然的圖書館。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  從這方面來說，既不無聊，也不會寂寞。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這麼說你在這裡上班還挺開心的囉？", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不是的，普羅旺斯姐姐。只在室內進行檢測與研究，不是地質學。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  分析其他天災信使帶來的土壤泥巴中的成分情況，並分析天災可能性，也不是地質學。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  地靈前輩現在所用的設備是可攜式的，功能十分簡陋，是外出勘探採樣時使用的。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我和我的設備最近一直待在室內，只是因為天災信使們需要我，羅德島需要我而已。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不過最近的工作也有點太多了吧？為什麼連一些不熟的天災信使都跑來找我要報告了？", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  作為天災信使，預測錯了以後，心裡還是會很不好受。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你的報告也可以讓我們對結果有一個大致的預估。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  一般這種報告都是找學者寫的，專業程度先不提，經常會出現報告內容並不是工作所需的情況。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  而你除了是優秀的地質學家，本身也是一位非常厲害的天災信使。", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  所以哪怕......", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哪怕不需要給雇主看，也會想要一份來作參考。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  噢？怪不得我的工作量變大了，原來還有這一部分原因啊。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嘿嘿嘿嘿！多虧了我！你的名氣已經在天災信使當中傳開了！", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  “那位範克圖爾的大師”，他們都這麼叫你。是不是超級有格調？", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那也就是說，前面幾次你叫我做的事......", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那些莫名其妙的加班......", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_145_prove_1", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊對了，我得去洗澡了，文件就先放這裡啦——", "name": "普羅旺斯"}, "figure_art": "char_145_prove_1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 300.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "char_183_skgoat_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.6}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你給我站住！", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  糟糕，我腿麻了。", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  前輩，要不要我幫你去追！", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "char_180_amgoat"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1", "name2": "char_180_amgoat", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不用，我走幾步就不麻了！你休息一下！", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_183_skgoat_1"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  腳......啊......好麻......", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  普羅旺斯！你給我站住！", "name": "地靈"}, "figure_art": "char_183_skgoat_1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}